{"tid":2234574,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會腰痛加抖氣吸唔到盡？","createTime":"2020-10-08T04:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T08:26:38.000Z","uid":297638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a82e2ae7e2767ccc596901af38f9ec3950562d3b","tid":2234574,"uid":297638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"腰除啲陰啲痛就好多年，係肚臍高度，淨係左邊背既腰位<br />\n拉下筋條腰就啪啪下會舒服返一陣<br />\n但有時痛既同時，又會覺得抖氣時條氣吸唔到盡咁，硬係有野頂住咁既感覺 <br />\n以為照過xray又無異樣，醫生都話其實係坐姿同肌肉問題 ... <br />\n抖氣方面，其實我諗醫生唔係好明我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以幫唔到我<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無巴打明我係指啲乜... sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"f2f8726867ac9d26b5370a1730ebf72407ee6820","tid":2234574,"uid":26811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"近排買左個腰按板, 用後感覺好似好左好多, 你可以買來試試"},{"pid":"9caf3e1d08f47d52febbaacea734ae87b4f0c6fe","tid":2234574,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"脊柱側彎？"},{"pid":"c267865faa1a584f9199b4c36397722a0fdeee14","tid":2234574,"uid":297638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9caf3e1d08f47d52febbaacea734ae87b4f0c6fe","tid":2234574,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"脊柱側彎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"輕微，但醫生話唔關事"},{"pid":"5afe0fb721f38443e06e22f6c88e27b7e920a49f","tid":2234574,"uid":297638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2f8726867ac9d26b5370a1730ebf72407ee6820","tid":2234574,"uid":26811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"近排買左個腰按板, 用後感覺好似好左好多, 你可以買來試試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"咩黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e524ed5c4125cc39a9530e5ec41659dcfe652057","tid":2234574,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"抖氣方面我都有<br />\n冬